<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stay-n">stay <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /steɪ/    美 /steɪ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>停留；暂住：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>short stay</strong> in hospital 
短期住院</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I visited a lot of temples during my stay in Kyoto. 
我在京都逗留期间参观了许多寺庙。</p></div></div>